`ROADMAP.md` is written at the project root. It has 5 phases — hardened MVP → self-serve onboarding → trust/transparency → multi-tournament → growth/billing — each with checkbox deliverables, concrete exit criteria, and a dependency map at the bottom. All 12 research docs were incorporated (Clerk for auth, SportsData.io for data, versioned config snapshots, Zod+RHF for validation, append-only audit log, etc.).